longBusinessSummary: 7C Solarparken AG owns and operates PV farms primarily in Germany and Belgium. The company has a combined asset portfolio of 339 MWp. The company was formerly known as Colexon Energy, AG and changed its name to 7C Solarparken AG in January 2015. 7C Solarparken AG is headquartered in Bayreuth, Germany.
